data.name: label13.Text
data.value:
*Pharma is the Role with the Lowesr level of access.
*Pharma can add Medecine and access all item in the Medicine Toolbar.
*This means that Pharma can't control Setting like the Design Etc.
*They can Add and Delete Medecine and can Approve Validity and Expired of Deny Medecine.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value:
*Admin is the Role with the highest level of access.
*Admin can add content and access all item in the Admin Toolbar.
*This means that Admins can control Setting like the Design Etc.
*They can Add and Delete other Admin Users and can Approve or Deny Edits Made by User.
